#- Kill,

Your puppy is super adorable.  It makes me want to get another puppy.  :3

We will have to either hire a detective or become detectives in order to solve the case of the stolen horses.
#- Regarding pumpkins and Duck City, perhaps you can help me with a great pumpkining.  And if that goes well, perhaps you could assist me further in Pumptopia related activies.

Yours,
PumpQueen Jacky
